Learning Outcome

Through this assignment, I gained a clear understanding of semantic similarity and how words can be related in different ways. I also learned to identify various types of relationships such as synonyms, near synonyms, category-based connections, and contextual associations. This concept is important in natural language processing, where understanding word meaning plays a key role in tasks like text analysis and machine learning.